{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it illegal to smoke on hospital grounds",
        "additional_details": "We think patients across the country are being subjected to second hand smoke when going to medical appointments. We think this should not be a risk when attending a hospital appointment, especially on an \u201csmoke-free site\u201d. We think the Tobacco & Vapes Bill 2024 has missed this vital point.",
        "background": "We want the government to make it against the law to smoke on hospital grounds, with fines for offenders.",
